name: Asistencia Programa Social y Evento
query:
SELECT
    pse.name AS "Programa:Link/Programa Social y Evento:150",
    pse.descripcion AS "Descripción:Data:250",
    pse.fecha_inicial_evento AS "Fecha Inicial:Date:120",
    pse.fecha_final_evento AS "Fecha Final:Date:120",
    pse.tipo_programa AS "Tipo de Programa:Data:150",
    pse.sector_poblacional AS "Sector Poblacional:Data:150",
    psed.name AS "Detalle ID:Link/Programa Social y Evento Detalle:150",
    psed.beneficiario_id AS "Beneficiario ID:Data:120",
    psed.cui_beneficiario AS "CUI Beneficiario:Data:150",
    psed.customer_name AS "Nombre del Beneficiario:Data:200",
    psed.doc_link AS "Documento:Data:200"
FROM
    `tabPrograma Social y Evento` pse
LEFT JOIN
    `tabPrograma Social y Evento Detalle` psed
    ON psed.parent = pse.name
ORDER BY
    pse.name, psed.idx;
